<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹一直想要登上舞台，但绝不是像现在这个样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他被悄悄地卖给了一个马戏团。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是那些马戏团的人一点都不友善。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，驴，晚饭就吃些稻草吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>训练师把稻草扔到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹尝了一点稻草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>稻草吃起来很干，就像沙子一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯昂。”他抱怨着把它吐了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么，你不喜欢稻草？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好吧，那吃些干草吧。”训练师说着把干草扔到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹尝了一点干草，它尝起来像稻草一样糟糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯昂，嗯昂。”匹诺曹抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你等着吧，小驴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你饿的时候就什么都吃了。”训练师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，他抽打了匹诺曹的腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天，训练师都会让匹诺曹训练。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跳过这个圈。用两条腿走路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跳恰恰。顶着球。装死。”他大喊着挥动鞭子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果匹诺曹犯了错误，训练师就会鞭打他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，训练师说道，“小驴子，今晚是你第一次表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你做得好，我就会喂你葡萄吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要你犯一点错，你就什么都吃不到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马戏团的帐篷里都是人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的座位都坐满了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“女士们先生们，欢迎来到维托马戏团。”马戏团老板说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是维托，我们今晚有一个特别的演出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这头驴从西班牙千里迢迢赶来为您表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为国王和王后表演过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他也为公爵和贵族们表演过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他震惊了欧洲所有的孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观众们欢呼着鼓掌，匹诺曹开始表演他的技能。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，他用两条腿走路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他顶着球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观众笑了，匹诺曹能看到那些开心的孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后，他跳起了恰恰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹又向观众们看去，他看到一个蓝色头发的女人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹跳过铁圈从帐篷里跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观众欢呼着，匹诺曹跑啊跑啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹一直跑到海边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蓝色小仙女就站在海边！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，蓝色小仙女，帐篷里的那个人是你吗？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，匹诺曹。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我真惭愧。我太傻了，我不是一个好孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很抱歉。你能帮助我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你很后悔，匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我不能再帮助你了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须为你犯的错误付出代价。”她难过地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我不想永远做一头驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想做回男孩儿。我想回学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想救杰佩托。”他哭着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许你以后能做那些事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是首先，你必须弥补犯下的错误。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你是怎么变成驴的？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我自私而懒惰。”匹诺曹回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，如果你现在开始做完全相反的事，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你就会变回木头男孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说完话，就消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘与自私和懒惰相反的是慷慨和勤劳吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要怎么做才能成为慷慨而勤劳的人呢？’他思索着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹想出了一个好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>